This paper is primarily focused on image generation using GANs, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves human interaction and feedback, which could be categorized under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the use of constraints and semantic spaces involves machine learning techniques such as reinforcement learning and optimization, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the optimization of GANs, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR).
